<div ana="#b1" corresp="#hamm0054.diplomatic #hamm0054.translation" subtype="transcription" type="edition" xml:id="hamm0054.transcription">
<p>
+ Ἐπὶ Ἀβδάλλα Μαάυια ἀμήρα<lb/>
ἀλμουμενὴν ἀπελ<add>ο</add>ύθη <expan>
<abbr>κ</abbr>
<ex>αὶ</ex>
</expan> ἀνε<lb/>
