		  </p>
</div>
<div ana="#b1" corresp="#hamm0054.diplomatic #hamm0054.transcription" type="translation" xml:id="hamm0054.translation">
<p>In the days of <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p01" xml:lang="x-Arabic ">Abdallah Mu'awiya</persName>, the <rs type="religTitle">commander of the faithful</rs>, the clibanus of the <add>baths</add> here was cleared and renewed by <name>
<persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p02" xml:lang="x-Arabic ">Abdallah </persName>
<rs type="family">son </rs> of <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p03" xml:lang="x-Arabic ">Abu Hashim </persName>
</name>, the <rs type="admTitle">governor</rs>, in the <date>month of December, on the fifth day, Monday, in the 6th year of the indiction, in the year 726 of the colony, according to the Arabs the 42nd year</date>, for the healing of the sick, under the care of <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p04">John </persName> the <rs type="ethnicon">Gadarene</rs>, the <rs type="occupation">steward</rs>.</p>
</div>
